The paper deals with protein classification using deep learning and 2D representations. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) also suggests that it could belong to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and deep learning (cs.DL) sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with protein structures and their classification, which suggests that it could also belong to the bioinformatics (cs.BIO) sub-category.
